I would expect to see more grain instances....

For example- grains are intended to be lightswitch, and long-lived.

So.... each "node" should itself, be a grain. And it should spin up children as it needs for its data, ie modbus grain, mqtt grain, etc.

Parents should own and manage their children.

Also, each instance... should be its own grain. Graints shouldn't be enumerating through lists of items to poll.... They should be their own grains.

